und\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid#%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E6%80%A7\">https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid#%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E6%80%A7</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/../img/css-grid/1.png\" alt=\"20220414成都\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"使用\"><a href=\"#使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用\"></a>使用</h1><h2 id=\"display-grid-inline-grid\"><a href=\"#display-grid-inline-grid\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"display: grid | inline-grid \"></a><code>display: grid | inline-grid </code></h2><ul>\n<li><code>grid</code><ul>\n<li>该元素的行为类似块级元素并且根据网格模型布局它的内容。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>inline-grid</code><ul>\n<li>元素的行为类似于内联元素并且它的内容根据网格盒模型布局。</li>\n<li>它等同于 <code>inline grid</code>。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"相关属性\"><a href=\"#相关属性\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"相关属性\"></a>相关属性</h2><h3 id=\"grid\"><a href=\"#grid\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"grid\"></a><code>grid</code></h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>grid 是一个 CSS 简写属性，可以用来设置以下属性：</p>\n<p>显式网格属性： grid-template-rows、grid-template-columns 和 grid-template-areas。</p>\n<p>隐式网格属性： grid-auto-rows、grid-auto-columns 和 grid-auto-flow。</p>\n<p>间距属性： grid-column-gap 和 grid-row-gap。</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"grid-template-rows\"><a href=\"#grid-template-rows\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"grid-template-rows\"></a><code>grid-template-rows</code></h3><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 